	<h2><a href="/posts/more-workers-needed-in-the-kitchen:48a9a686-d298-4bd1-927e-2d084834cda3">More workers needed in the kitchen</a></h2>	<div class="posted-on">
		<p>Posted on 18/8/08 by 
		<a href="/felix">Felix Geisendörfer</a>				</p>
		<div class="thumb">
			<img alt="" src="/img/felix_thumb.jpg"/>		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="body">
				<p>Hey folks,</p>
<p>there are new <a href="http://debuggable.com/posts/3-jobs-for-skilled-bakers:484fa544-0758-48d0-82a7-6fe44834cda3">jobs in the world of CakePHP</a>. The <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/index/48075b46-da18-4009-a658-83a14dddecbf">CakePHP job board</a> has seen the following additions:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.about.com/">About.com</a> is looking to fill a <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/view/48a2f2d7-8bdc-4f6c-bf78-1e7445591f8c">Senior Ad Systems Developer</a> position.
<li><a href="http://www.makatto.com/">Makatto.com</a> is looking for <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/view/485d441b-e0c8-45ea-9237-5dc845591f8c">candidates experienced with PHP, Mysql & JS</a>.
<li><a href="http://www.eks.com">EKS</a> is based in Switzerland and looking for <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/view/488ed528-13a0-4a22-b98f-247e45591f8c">LAMP Bakers</a> to join their team.</li>
<li><a href="http://bluechipapps.com/">Blue Chip</a> has opportunities for <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/view/48482c76-7cd4-4bc9-b031-4e0c45591f8c">cake bakers</a> who are also experienced in either Django or Rails.</li>
</ul>
<p>If any of those jobs sound interesting to you, <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/index/48075b46-da18-4009-a658-83a14dddecbf">go ahead and apply</a>. If you are looking for skilled bakers yourself, consider <a href="http://www.eliteopensourcejobs.com/jobs/add/community_id:48075b46-da18-4009-a658-83a14dddecbf">posting on the job board</a>. Posting is as cheap as $75 for a 7 day post of which 50% are donated to the <a href="http://cakefoundation.org/">Cake Software Foundation</a>.</p>
<p>-- Felix Geisendörfer aka the_undefined</p>
<p><img style="display: none;" src="http://debuggable.com/posts/tick/48a9a686-d298-4bd1-927e-2d084834cda3"></p>
